WEBVTT

00:07:59.131 --> 00:08:01.898
and we put the crown on his 
head and we blew the bubbles,

00:08:01.898 --> 00:08:04.339
and then I asked him, I said,

00:08:04.339 --> 00:08:08.795
"So what are you going to do now?"

00:08:08.795 --> 00:08:10.605
And he answered,

00:08:10.605 --> 00:08:12.238
"Make friends."

00:08:12.238 --> 00:08:14.350
And he did.

00:08:14.350 --> 00:08:17.904
He started volunteering 
and he made friends there,

00:08:17.904 --> 00:08:20.590
and he began going to a church
and he made friends there,

00:08:20.590 --> 00:08:23.550
and at Christmas he invited my husband
and me to a party in his apartment,

00:08:23.550 --> 00:08:28.667
and the place was filled with his friends.

00:08:28.667 --> 00:08:30.910
Claim your experience.